data.description: Welcome to Julington Creek Plantation! With wonderful amenities and St. Johns school district, this home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. The front entrance opens to the living room and the master is off to the right side. Two other bedrooms are located on the other side of the living room, offering some privacy from the master suite, perfect for family and/or guest rooms. The nice-sized fenced back yard features a covered lanai and plenty of room for hosting the perfect family barbecue. This golf-course community has active plans to update all the amenities including plans for a new club house and lazy river. With tennis courts, playgrounds, club house with pool, splash pad and snack bar, the entertainments is a walk away.
